However, none of these books is essential to the play of the game. All that is absolutely necessary for playing are the core rules: the }{\i\fs24 Player's Handbook}{\fs24  and the }{\i\fs24 DUNGEON MASTER\'99 Guide}{\fs24  (}{\i\fs24 DMG}{\fs24 
). The other }{\i\fs24 PHBR}{\fs24  books are recapped below, and their usefulness to elf PCs is explained.
