\par }{\b\fs24\cf13 Half-Elf
\par }{\fs24 
\par \tab Half-elves, as noted earlier, are not truly a subrace of elves. They have no adjustments or advantages and disadvantages to note here, although a DM may wish to make an exception in special cases.
\par 
