\par \tab }{\b\fs24 Ability Score Adjustments:}{\fs24  Because their lives are spent in constant exertion, wood elves are stronger than other elves. However, they are less sociable because of their upbringing. They have bonuses of +1 to Strength an
d Dexterity and penalties of \endash 1 to Constitution and Charisma.
